Package: sparkr
Title: Gives an idea or spark of inspiration for an activity to do
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Liam", "Surry", , "surryl@mcmaster.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A package for giving you a random idea of something to do when you are lacking inspiration. Ideas are predetermined in a list and randomly selected for you to enjoy. Arguments for this function are simply TRUE or FALSE. 
License: CC BY 4.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
